strings.Value: "Well, ladies and gentlemen! Want to place any bets on whether our wet-nosed Sarenrae follower will ever put in an appearance?"
"He hurt me so much... but I still hope we see him again! At least to hear his explanation."
"There is only one thing that is certain in this life. And I think you know what I'm talking about..."
"He will hardly have the nerve to stand before us, after what he's done. Anyway, you should never underestimate traitors."
"I hope he has enough decency never to show his face again... But on the other hand, I don't suppose he has any decency."
"I hope he has enough decency never to show his face again... But on the other hand, I don't suppose he has any decency."
